# Week 5 — Day 4: CloudTrail → CloudWatch Logs → Alarms

## Goal
Send CloudTrail IAM events to CloudWatch Logs, create metric filters, and alert via SNS.

## Evidence
```bash
aws cloudtrail get-trail --name "$TRAIL_NAME" --query 'Trail.{LogGroupArn:CloudWatchLogsLogGroupArn,RoleArn:CloudWatchLogsRoleArn,IsMultiRegion:IsMultiRegionTrail}'
aws logs describe-metric-filters --log-group-name "/aws/cloudtrail/iam-events" --query 'metricFilters[].{Name:filterName,Pattern:filterPattern}'
aws cloudwatch describe-alarms --alarm-names ALARM-RootLogin ALARM-UnauthorizedApi ALARM-IamChange --query 'MetricAlarms[].{Name:AlarmName,Metric:MetricName,NS:Namespace,Actions:AlarmActions}'
